nodes.text: Elaine Baker (born December 23, 1952) is the ex-wife of make-up designer Rick Baker. During the filming of the second Star Wars film, Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back, Baker was filmed for test shots of Emperor Palpatine. However, Marjorie Eaton would be the one to appear in the final film.
